Actually, `IntObjectHashMap` extends `AbstractMutableIntObjectMap` which extends `AbstractMutableIntCollection`... It should have `isEmpty()` from `RichIterable` or `Map`. Yes, all collections have `isEmpty()`.

So the optimization is simple: in `RiskEngine.placeExchangeOrder`, wrap the futures margin loop with `if (!userProfile.positions.isEmpty())`.

